                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center"><span class="style45">Eila's 5th Year of Poetry ! </span></div></td>
                                      </tr>
                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center">
                                          <p>Eila Webster, our local poet, enters her 5th year of penning a new poem every month for us to enjoy. Her latest composition: <a href="PDF Pages/Monthly Poems/2019 February.pdf" target="_blank"><span class="style46"><strong>The month of Subtle Change </strong></span></a>reminds us that Winter isn't over yet but that Spring is just around the corner ! </p>
                                          <p>Click the image below to enter Eila's world of poetry . . . </p>
                                        </div></td>
