                                      </tr>
                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center">
                                          <table width="720">
                                            <tr>
                                              <td width="399"><div align="center">The <strong>Westmuir Annual Prize Draw</strong> was held recently in the village hall accompanied by music, mulled wine and mince pies; a much enjoyed combination. All 500 hundred tickets were sold and the lucky winners were as follows: Large Hamper: <strong>Hazel Innes</strong>, Westmuir. Medium Hamper: <strong>Findlay Doig</strong>, Kirriemuir. Small Hamper:<strong> Iris Forrest</strong>, Kirriemuir. Thanks to all who contributed items for these three fantastic prizes and for everyone's support again this year, , especially to Ian, Ann and Jim who worked so hard to make it such a success.</div></td>
                                              <td width="309"><div align="center"><img src="images/Raffle 2018.jpg" alt="Raffle2018" name="Raffle2018" width="300" height="200" border="1" id="Raffle2018" /></div></td>
