                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center" class="style45">The Pop-Up Pulled Pork ! </div></td>
                                      </tr>
                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center">
                                          <table width="720">
                                            <tr>
                                              <td width="227"><div align="center"><img src="images/Pop Up Cafe 2018.jpg" alt="" name="carpark2018" width="262" height="175" border="1" id="carpark2018" /></div></td>
                                              <td width="10"><div align="center"></div></td>
                                              <td width="424"><div align="center">
                                                <p align="center">The Hall committee would like to thank all the helpers, folks who donated, and customers who came along to the Pop-Up cafe on Saturday.  The total made for the hall maintenance funds &amp; village defibrillator is <strong>&pound;522</strong>. This will make a substantial contribution to hall insurance costs for the year and will help with some of the upfront costs of a defibrillator. </p>
                                                </div></td>
                                            </tr>
                                          </table>
                                        </div></td>
                                      </tr>
                                      
                                      
                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center">
                                          <p align="center">Customers for the cafe came from the village and even crossed the border from Kirrie to sample the menu which consisted of a choice of five mouth-watering soups, filled rolls, pizza, quiche, salad and the main draw; <strong>The Downies&rsquo; Pulled Pork &amp; Focaccia!</strong> </p>
                                          <p align="center">If you missed these treats, hopefully another cafe will be planned in the future, if the committee have enough volunteer helpers!</p>
                                        </div></td>
                                      </tr>
