                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center" class="style45"><span class="style46">New Feature</span> - Local Community Policing Area Report </div></td>
                                      </tr>
                                      <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><div align="center">
                                          <p>Now that Westmuir has a full representative on <strong>Kirriemuir Landward West Community Council</strong>, we have access to the latest <strong>Local Area Police Reports</strong> which are submitted to their meetings as a way of keeping local communities aware of any current areas or issues of concern. </p>
                                          <p>You can <a href="PDF Pages/Police Reports/Police 11-2018.pdf" target="_blank">Read the November 2018 Report Here</a>. </p>
                                          <p>We already have a link at the bottom of our left column which will take you to KLWCC's own website where you can also read minutes of recent <strong>Community Council Meetings</strong>. </p>
                                        </div></td>
                                      </tr>
                                      
                                      

                                      
